&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECEPTION SUPERVISOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Full Time Reception Supervisor required.  The position will be based across both sites, Gloucester Health Access Centre and Matson Lane Surgery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The ideal candidate will have experience in providing excellent customer service and supervisory support to a small team. They will be required to greet patients, maintain records, provide support to clinical staff and carry out a range of clerical, administrative and supervisory processes. Working as part of a friendly team, you will be self-motivated and willing to help out in other areas of the business, as required.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;It is essential that the candidate is computer literate. Knowledge of the NHS in a primary care setting would be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salary will be dependent on experience, NHS pension and additional health benefits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date:  20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; November 2020      Interview date: 27&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; November 2020 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For general enquiries please contact Ann Rebello on 01452 336290.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
